The paper focuses on generating high-resolution images using GANs, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The authors also mention using an autoencoder to learn the intrinsic high-level structure of real images, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the quality of the generated images in terms of perceptual photo-realism, which is related to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
